<h4><strong>1. From Incheon airport to Hoam</strong></h4>
<p>① Take the '#6017 airport limousine bus' at the <span style="color:initial">Gate 6B (Terminal 1) or Gate 27 (terminal 2)</span>. (Check the bus time table). <span style="color:initial">The bus will depart every 30~40 minutes. It takes about 110 minutes by the bus (15,000 KRW by cash).</span> <br>

② Get off at the last stop 'Hoam Faculty House' </p>
<a href="http://www.hoam.ac.kr/eng/hoamHotel/airportbus_pop.php">6017 Airport limousine bus Timetable (http://www.hoam.ac.kr/eng/hoamHotel/airportbus_pop.php)</a>
