<h4><strong>2. From Gimpo airport to Hoam</strong></h4>
<p>① Take the '#6003 Airport limousine bus' at the Bus terminal #6. The bus will depart every 20
    minutes. <span style="color:initial">It takes about 60 minutes by bus (About 4,000 KRW by cash).</span><br>
② Get off at the main gate of Seoul National University. <span style="color:initial">Take a taxi or a shuttle for Hoam faculty house at the main gate. </span> Shuttle service is available upon reservation only, Running hour of shuttle: 08:00 ~ 19:00 (Monday to Friday). Please contact at 82-2-880-0311 for reservation.<br>
</p>
		<br>	
		<br>	
<h4><strong>3. by Taxi</strong></h4>
<p>① Take a taxi from Incheon/Gimpo airport to Hoam Faculty House (HFH).<p>
